EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 2100Z DAILY
   23 AND 24 MAR WITHIN 62 MILES OF 57-38N 009-27W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MESSAGE 242200Z MAR 13.
